            <title>[HBASE-14039] BackupHandler.deleteSnapshot MUST use HBase Snapshot API </title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HBASE-14039</link>
                <project id="12310753" key="HBASE">HBase</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;BackupHandler.deleteSnapshot MUST use HBase API for that (HBaseAdmin) - not direct FS access (deleting snapshot folder may be not enough?).&lt;/p&gt;</description>
